p:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mua Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Paul Pogba chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Paul Pogba nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Camp Nou b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU mua Milinkovic-Savic thay Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU mua Milinkovic-Savic thay Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Chi-120-trieu-euro,-MU-mua-Milinkovic-Savic-thay-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Pogba m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola c\u1ee7a Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t,&nbsp;Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U sau qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Pogba mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed y\u00eau th\u00edch, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng anh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU nh\u1eafm Milinkovic-Savic thay Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo CalcioMercato.com, MU mua Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Paul Pogba chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/milinkovicsavic-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU nh\u1eafm Milinkovic-Savic thay Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-120-trieu-euro-ac-milan-tinh-vuot-mat-mu-vu-pogba-serbia-172-193722.html\" target=\"_blank\">AC Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic</span>, song l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Lazio th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Real v\u00e0 Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia. Theo CalcioMercato.com, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMilinkovic-Savic \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2065","checkdouble":"193895"},{"date":"06:47 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qarabag vs BATE Borisov 00h00 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-qarabag-vs-bate-borisov-00h00-ngay-88-champions-league-201819.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qarabag vs BATE Borisov l\u00fac 00h00 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qarabag vs BATE Borisov 00h00 ng\u00e0y 88 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qarabag vs BATE Borisov 00h00 ng\u00e0y 88 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Qarabag-vs-BATE-Borisov.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Qarabag vs BATE Borisov</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Qarabag vs BATE Borisov: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Qarabag \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Azerbaijan \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Champions League. R\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Roma, Atletico v\u00e0 Chelsea song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 2 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 Qarabag \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u00eam nay, v\u1edbi \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc BATE Borisov. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng Qarabag s\u1ebd c\u00f3 90 ph\u00fat d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 BATE Borisov r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2011-12 t\u1edbi nay, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Belarus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Belarus \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra n\u00ean BATE Borisov r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ea1ch 10 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngo\u00e0i ra do \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Belarus v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u00ean BATE \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i bung s\u1ee9c cho Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u1edf Azerbaijan v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a kh\u1edfi tranh. Trong 1 th\u00e1ng qua, Qarabag ch\u1ec9 tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i Champions League. Do kh\u00f4ng c\u1ecd x\u00e1t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c n\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gurban Gurbanov thi\u1ebfu c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9. 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Qarabag \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 thua theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Do v\u1eady, BATE Borisov ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Azerbaijan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9/10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qarabag ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, 3/5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a BATE Borisov c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Qarabag (4-2-3-1): Halldorsson - Medvedev, Sadygov, Guseynov, Guerrier - Garayev, Slavchev - Quintana, Michel, Zoubir - Emeghara.<br>\r\n+ BATE Borisov (4-3-3): Shcherbitski - Rios, Filipenko, Filipovic, Volodjko - Yablonski, Baga, Dragun - Ivanic, Stasevich, Signevich.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2064","checkdouble":"193896"},{"date":"16:48 06/08","title":"HLV Bayern n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin Boateng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U quan t\u00e2m?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/hlv-kovac-ngoi-khen-jerome-boateng.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Niko Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jerome Boateng. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Man United trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Boateng \u0111\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Jerome Boateng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Paris Saint-Germain li\u00ean h\u1ec7. Ch\u00ednh Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Man United mu\u1ed1n mua Boateng. Kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1 su\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Niko Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jerome Boateng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Niko Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jerome Boateng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/hlv-kovac-ngoi-khen-jerome-boateng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jerome Boateng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kovac b\u00e0ng quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh M.U t\u1ea1i Munich. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 nh\u1edd pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Javi Martinez ph\u00fat 59. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Boateng ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7p 2 sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay Mats Hummels sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, HLV Niko Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jerome Boateng. \u201cV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Boateng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin g\u00ec m\u1edbi\u201d, \u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Boateng \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Bayern. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBoateng t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2010/11 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Anh gia nh\u1eadp Bayern t\u1eeb N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 6 danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Bundesliga, 1 t\u1ea1i Champions League. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Boateng v\u1edbi Bayern c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2021.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/that-bai-vu-mina-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-nguoi-thay-the-172-193829.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Mina, MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\">MU thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern, Mourinho ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tro-thanh-dong-doi-messi-vidal-len-tieng-cam-on-hum-xam-180-193716.html\">Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Messi, Vidal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n H\u00f9m x\u00e1m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/zambrano-phat-bieu-ve-tan-binh-bayern-alphonso-davies-193-193707.html\">Bayern c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial-172-193655.html\">Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i thanh l\u00fd sao v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt gi\u00fap M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2063","checkdouble":"193857"},{"date":"16:30 06/08","title":"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m \"h\u00e0ng hot\" Bundesliga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/xac-nhan-arsenal-va-chelsea-quan-tam-leon-bailey.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Leon Bailey \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayer Leverkusen. Ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Leon-Bailey-noi-ve-tuong-lai-truoc-tin-don-duoc-Chelsea-quan-tam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bailey x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Chelsea, Man City, Arsenal v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f2i 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/bailey-danh-tieng-voi-chelsea-va-arsenal-172-191957.html\" target=\"_blank\">Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 Bayer Leverkusen. Hi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Leon Bailey mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga c\u00f9ng Leverkusen</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Leverkusen thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Bundesliga v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, Bayer Leverkusen k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Bayern Munich t\u1edbi 29 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/xac-nhan-arsenal-va-chelsea-quan-tam-leon-bailey.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leon Bailey mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga c\u00f9ng Leverkusen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 song Leon Bailey mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga c\u00f9ng Leverkusen \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Bayern Munich l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga, Leverkusen hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2062","checkdouble":"193859"},{"date":"16:06 06/08","title":"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Myanmar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00f4ng Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV\u00a0Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Oman trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 5/8 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m b\u1edfi pha v\u1ea9y m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng sinh n\u0103m 1999 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng xo\u00e1y l\u00ean cao r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed9n xu\u1ed1ng theo h\u00ecnh v\u00f2ng cung, r\u00f3t v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1ebft khung th\u00e0nh Oman.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1eadu</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n theo ki\u1ec3u Trivela n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00ean Vnexpress: \u201c\u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh trong kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng g\u1ed1c Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u00d4ng Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eady c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f3 hai \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i trong x\u1eed l\u00fd. Th\u1ee9 hai, \u0111\u00f4i khi V\u0103n H\u1eadu n\u00f3ng t\u00ednh, v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 tranh c\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 pha va ch\u1ea1m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng h\u00f4m 23/6. T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 'c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm' c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i song anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i U19 cho t\u1edbi \u0110TQG. \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o th\u00ec V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i Lan lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-indonesia-mat-ngoi-sao-sang-gia-nhat-tai-asiad-2018-168-193851.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/6/9/video-ban-thang-u23-indonesia-20-u23-philippines-vong-bang-seagame-28.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-indonesia-mat-ngoi-sao-sang-gia-nhat-tai-asiad-2018-168-193851.html\">\u0110T Olympic Indonesia m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao lai Ezra Walian v\u00ec l\u00fd do CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n RKC Waalwijk kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2061","checkdouble":"193860"},{"date":"16:46 06/08","title":"Barca b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal v\u1ee5 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" 105 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/barca-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal-vu-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Dembele</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ousmane Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Barca chi ra, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Barca-chan-duong-Arsenal-mua-Ousmane-Dembele--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ousmane Dembele ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi Barca \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Camp Nou \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele</span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, n\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 85 tri\u1ec7u euro. Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ousmane Dembele kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele co the roi Camp Nou neu Barca mua Willian\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Giam-doc-the-thao-Barca-chot-tuong-lai-Dembele-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Ousmane Dembele\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb RAC1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u0169ng\u00a0mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Dembele v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca coi Ousmane Dembele l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Malcom, Coutinho, Arthur, Clement Lenglet v\u00e0 Umtiti l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Barca trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Dembele \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua t\u00f4i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2060","checkdouble":"193861"},{"date":"16:38 06/08","title":"Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/jurgen-klopp-khong-dat-muc-tieu-vo-dich-cho-liverpool-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 chi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</h2><h2>Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ra h\u01a1n 160 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Alisson Becker, Fabinho, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. The Kop c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o ngo\u00e0i Emre Can, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung b\u1eb1ng hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp khong dat muc tieu vo dich cho Liverpool mua toi.\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/jurgen-klopp-khong-dat-muc-tieu-vo-dich-cho-liverpool-mua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u: &quot;Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, r\u1ed3i t\u1ef1 s\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e2u n\u00f3i '\u1ed3, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ea5y'.&quot;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trong t\u1eebng tu\u1ea7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi khi g\u1eb7p West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111ang b\u1ecb lo ng\u1ea1i khi m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joel Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00f4ng, c\u00f2n Ragnar Klavan d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo. C\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Napoli \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Dejan Lovren \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p West Ham do th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 Klopp cho bi\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Trung v\u1ec7 ngo\u00e0i Croatia \u00edt nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-co-the-no-them-bom-tan-cho-liverpool-172-193799.html\">Klopp h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n n\u1ed5 th\u00eam bom t\u1ea5n &ldquo;ph\u00fat 89&rdquo; cho Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-liverpool-dat-dau-hoi-ve-tan-binh-alisson-172-193787.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ancelotti-bo-hop-bao-sau-tham-bai-truoc-liverpool-176-193747.html\">Ancelotti b\u1ecf h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193740.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 5-0 Napoli (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robbie-fowler-nhan-xet-liverpool-mua-toi-se-rat-dang-so-172-193729.html\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\">Liverpool 5-0 Napoli: The Klopp h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A trong ng\u00e0y Alisson ra m\u1eaft</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2059","checkdouble":"193862"}]}